description: What began as a “wouldn’t it be fun if…” conversation between two buddies is now a thriving restaurant in the Austin foodie scene, and now their food trailer is taking the same beloved Mexican cuisine out to the streets. Mighty Bird supplies a wide variety of taco, burrito, and torta goodness; all made with premium ingredients, and all the tortillas and salsas are housemade and delicious.So if any of you Austinites are seeking an absolutely delightful meal, fly your way over to Mighty Bird because these burritos are the real deal.
name: Mighty Bird
